  "ADT vs implementation": "ADT vs implementation",
  "An ADT says what operations exist. An implementation decides how those operations work internally.": "ADT 說明有哪些操作；implementation 決定內部怎麼做到那些操作。",
  "Array vs ArrayList": "Array vs ArrayList",
  "An array has fixed length. An ArrayList grows by managing a backing array.": "array 長度固定；<code>ArrayList</code> 會管理底層 array，讓大小可以成長。",
  "Stack vs recursion": "Stack vs recursion",
  "Recursion uses the call stack. An explicit stack is a data structure you control.": "recursion 使用 call stack；explicit stack 是你自己控制的資料結構。",
  "BFS vs DFS": "BFS vs DFS",
  "BFS is layer-by-layer and good for unweighted shortest path. DFS goes deep and is good for structure exploration.": "BFS 一層一層走，適合 unweighted shortest path。DFS 會一路往深處走，適合探索結構。",
  "HashMap vs TreeMap": "HashMap vs TreeMap",
  "HashMap is expected O(1) but unordered. TreeMap is O(log n) and ordered.": "<code>HashMap</code> 期望是 <code>O(1)</code>，但沒有順序。<code>TreeMap</code> 是 <code>O(log n)</code>，但有排序。",
  "Heap vs BST": "Heap vs BST",
  "A heap gives fast priority removal but not full ordered search. A BST supports ordered search and traversal.": "heap 可以很快移除 priority 最高的項目，但不能做完整的有序搜尋。BST 支援有序搜尋和走訪。",
  "Greedy vs DP": "Greedy vs DP",
