  "DP vs graph shortest path": "DP vs graph shortest path",
  "DP usually has an acyclic dependency order. Graph shortest path handles more general connectivity and weights.": "DP 通常有不成環的 dependency 順序。Graph shortest path 可以處理更一般的連通性和 weight。",
  "Subarray vs subsequence": "Subarray vs subsequence",
