  "Name the expensive operation. Search, insert, delete, min/max, range query, connectivity, or repeated subproblem.": "<strong>說出昂貴操作。</strong>可能是 search、insert、delete、min/max、range query、connectivity，或重複子問題。",
  "Choose a structure or pattern. Use the tables above, then justify the choice.": "<strong>選資料結構或模式。</strong>用上面的表格，然後說明為什麼選它。",
  "Define the invariant. Examples: window is valid, heap parent is smaller, BST left is smaller, DP state means a specific subproblem.": "<strong>定義 invariant。</strong>例如 window 是合法的、heap parent 比 child 小、BST 左邊比較小、DP state 代表某個明確子問題。",
  "Write pseudocode. Keep it language-light before Java syntax gets in the way.": "<strong>寫 pseudocode。</strong>先不要被 Java 語法卡住。",
  "Implement in Java. Use clear helper methods and test small cases.": "<strong>用 Java 實作。</strong>使用清楚的 helper methods，並測小案例。",
  "Analyze complexity. Define variables and explain where the bound comes from.": "<strong>分析複雜度。</strong>定義變數，並說明 bound 從哪裡來。",
