  "Visit each vertex and edge once.": "每個 vertex 和 edge 都拜訪一次。",
  "Count table entries and work per entry.": "數 table entries，以及每個 entry 的工作量。",
  "What \"understanding\" should feel like": "真正理解應該長什麼樣子",
  "A student understands a topic when they can do four things without copying a template:": "學生如果不用抄模板就能做到下面四件事，才算真的理解一個主題：",
  "Explain why the structure or algorithm exists.": "說明這個資料結構或演算法為什麼存在。",
  "Trace a small example by hand.": "手動追一個小例子。",
  "Implement the core operation in Java.": "用 Java 實作核心操作。",
  "Analyze time and space complexity with defined variables.": "先定義變數，再分析時間和空間複雜度。",
  "If a solution feels like memorization, go back to the operation. DSA becomes clearer when every tool is tied to the operation it makes cheaper.": "如果解法像是在背，就回到操作本身。每個工具都對應到它讓哪個操作變便宜，DSA 會清楚很多。",
  "This page answers the question students ask most often: \"How do I know which structure to use?\" Start from the operation, then choose the structure.": "這頁回答學生最常問的問題：「我怎麼知道該用哪個結構？」先從操作出發，再選資料結構。",
  "Operation-first table": "先看操作的選擇表",
