  "Folders contain files and subfolders recursively.": "資料夾會遞迴包含檔案和子資料夾。",
  "Example: LRU cache design": "例子：LRU cache 設計",
  "A least-recently-used cache needs fast lookup and fast recency updates. A hash map gives O(1) key lookup. A doubly linked list gives O(1) remove and add-to-front when we already have the node.": "Least-recently-used cache 需要快速 lookup，也需要快速更新最近使用順序。hash map 提供 <code>O(1)</code> key lookup。當我們已經拿到 node 時，doubly linked list 可以 <code>O(1)</code> remove 和 add-to-front。",
  "This is a strong example of operation-first design: neither structure is enough alone, but together they match the required operations.": "這是很好的 operation-first design 例子：兩個結構單獨都不夠，但合在一起剛好符合需要的操作。",
  "Example: database index intuition": "例子：database index 直覺",
  "A balanced binary tree has logarithmic height, but each node has only two children. A B-tree-style index stores many keys per page and many children per node. That reduces the number of page reads, which is often the real bottleneck in storage systems.": "balanced binary tree 高度是對數，但每個 node 只有兩個 children。B-tree 風格的 index 會在每個 page 存很多 keys，也讓每個 node 有很多 children。這能減少 page reads，而 page reads 常常才是 storage system 真正的瓶頸。",
  "Reflection questions": "思考問題",
