  "For choosing a data structure or algorithm, start with the DSA Roadmap. This page is for extra references and practice support.": "如果要選資料結構或演算法，先看 <a href=\"roadmap.html\">DSA 路線圖</a>。這頁主要是額外參考與練習支援。",
